1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 c5 4. d5 d6 5. Nc3 exd5 6. cxd5 g6 7. Bf4 a6 8. a4 Bg7 9. h3 O-O 10. e3 Ne8 11. Be2 Nd7 12. O-O Qe7 13. Qd2 h6 $5 {the idea is to play g5 and f5} (13... Ne5 $5 14. Nxe5 dxe5 15. Bh2 Nd6 16. a5 Bd7 $132 17. e4 f5) 14. Bh2 (14. e4 $5 g5 15. Bh2 b6 $132) 14... f5 15. Qc2 g5 {active play by Black} 16. Nd2 f4 {Black got the f4 push in and in the meantime, White lost a tempo with Qd2-Qc2} 17. Nc4 Ne5 18. exf4 gxf4 19. f3 Nxc4 (19... Bf5 {was also possible}) 20. Bxc4 Be5 21. Rfe1 (21. Qg6+ Qg7 22. Qxg7+ Nxg7 {[%cal Gg7f5] we are also standing perfectly well in an endgame}) 21... Qg7 22. Kh1 Nf6 23. Bd3 Kh8 24. Be4 Bd7 25. Qd2 Rg8 26. Re2 Nh5 27. Qe1 Ng3+ 28. Bxg3 fxg3 29. Qf1 Raf8 30. Nd1 b5 31. a5 Rf4 32. Rc1 c4 33. Rcc2 Qf7 34. Rcd2 b4 35. Rc2 Bb5 36. Qe1 c3 37. bxc3 Bxe2 38. Qxe2 bxc3 39. Nxc3 Qc7 40. Nd1 Qxa5 41. Ra2 Qb5 42. Bd3 Qb3 43. Rxa6 Rd4 44. Nb2 Rh4 45. Nc4 Rxh3+ 46. Kg1 Bd4+ 47. Ne3 Bxe3+ 48. Qxe3 Qd1+ 49. Bf1 Rh1+ 50. Kxh1 Qxf1+ 0-1

