1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 c5 3. d5 e6 4. Nc3 exd5 5. cxd5 d6 6. Nf3 g6 7. Bf4 a6 8. Nd2 $5 {a rare but playable line !} Nbd7 (8... b5 $5 9. a4 Nh5 10. Be3 b4 11. Nce4 Bf5 $132 12. Bg5 Be7) 9. Qc2 (9. e4 b5 $132) (9. a4 $2 Nh5 10. Be3 Ne5 $17) 9... b5 10. a4 (10. Nce4 $6 Nb6 $15) (10. e4 $6 Nh5 11. Be3 Bg7 12. Be2 O-O $3 $15) 10... b4 (10... Nb6 $5) 11. Nce4 Nb6 $3 $132 12. Bg5 (12. Rd1 $5 Nbxd5 13. Bg5 Be7 14. Nc4 O-O 15. Nexd6 Be6 16. e4 Bxd6 17. exd5 Bf5 $11) 12... Be7 13. Bxf6 Bxf6 14. Nxf6+ Qxf6 15. e4 O-O 16. a5 Nd7 (16... Nxd5 $3 17. exd5 Re8+ 18. Kd1 Qd4 $17) 17. Be2 Re8 18. O-O Qd4 19. Rae1 b3 20. Nxb3 Qxe4 21. Qc3 Qf4 22. g3 Qf6 23. Nd2 Qxc3 24. bxc3 Nf6 25. Bf3 Bf5 26. Nc4 Bd3 27. Nxd6 Red8 28. Nb7 Rxd5 29. Bxd5 Nxd5 30. Nxc5 Bxf1 31. Kxf1 Nxc3 32. Re7 Rc8 33. Nd3 Nd5 34. Ra7 Rc6 35. Ne5 Rf6 36. Ng4 Re6 37. Nh6+ Kg7 38. Nxf7 Re7 39. Rxe7 Nxe7 40. Ne5 Kf6 41. Nd7+ Ke6 42. Nb8 Kd6 43. Ke2 Kc5 44. Nxa6+ Kb5 45. Nc7+ Kxa5 46. Ke3 Kb6 47. Ne6 Kc6 48. Ke4 Nd5 49. Ke5 Nb4 50. f4 Nd3+ 51. Kf6 Nf2 52. Kg7 Kd5 53. Ng5 Ng4 54. Kxh7 Nxh2 55. Kxg6 Ng4 56. Nf7 Ke4 57. Nh6 Ne3 58. f5 Kf3 59. f6 Nc4 60. g4 Kf4 61. f7 1-0

